Paper: hep-th/9404083

Date: 1994-04-14

Title: BFV Quantization of Relativistic Spinning Particles with a Single

Bosonic ConstraintAuthors: Silvio J. Rabello and Arvind N. Vaidya

Comments: 5 p., Latex, IF-UFRJ-94-14

Journal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A9 (1994) 1853-1856

Using the BFV approach we quantize a pseudoclassical model of the spin onehalf relativistic particle that contains a single bosonic constraint, contraryto the usual locally supersymmetric models that display first and second classconstraints.